WEBVTT

00:27.737 --> 00:29.345
Go Down in Flames.

00:31.701 --> 00:35.530
It means to end suddenly and completely.

00:38.975 --> 00:42.765
The project went down in flames because of lack of funds.

00:46.455 --> 00:50.981
The athlete's career went down in flames due to a major injury.

00:54.853 --> 00:59.605
The plan to go to the beach went down in flames when it suddenly rained.

